game.name: Elsa Restaurant Breakfast Management
game.description:
Having a delicious and healthy breakfast is a key to enjoy a happy and disease-free life. That is something that you should not miss out at all. When you have a good breakfast, it makes it easier for you to work with the boosted energy throughout the day. The beautiful princess Elsa has just opened up a new restaurant where various scrumptious dishes are served to her customers. Make sure that she is enough attentive to deliver the orders of all her customers timely.

Elsa Restaurant Breakfast Management is a free online cooking game under the girls category where you will have to help the princess to manage her brand new restaurant perfectly. Your good chef skills will surely help prepare and serve the mouth-watering dishes in the perfect manner. Happy customers will leave some coins on the counters that could help to increase the points in this brand new cooking game for girls and boys. 

You will find different varieties of breakfast there to serve to your customers. Check out the breakfast needs of the users before delivering them. The more they will look happy, the higher chances would be of obtaining the extra bonus points. Pick from the coffee, tea, toasted bread with butter, soup and more. Try to serve your order before the customers walk in with an angry mood. Earn the bonus points to ensure your victory in this cool html5 game for girls. Collect the maximum possible bonus points to clear the existing level and reach to the advanced level.
